Cell["\<\
r=3.;
Plot[{Re[Zf[r*Exp[\[ImaginaryI] theta]]],Im[Zf[r*Exp[\[ImaginaryI] \
theta]]]},{theta,0.,2 \[Pi]},PlotRange\[Rule]All]
Plot[{Re[ZAsymp[r*Exp[\[ImaginaryI] theta]]],Im[ZAsymp[r*Exp[\[ImaginaryI] \
theta]]]},{theta,0.,2 \[Pi]},PlotRange\[Rule]All]
Plot[{Re[Zf[r*Exp[\[ImaginaryI] theta]]-ZAsymp[r*Exp[\[ImaginaryI] \
theta]]],Im[Zf[r*Exp[\[ImaginaryI] theta]]-ZAsymp[r*Exp[\[ImaginaryI] \
theta]]]},{theta,0.,2 \[Pi]},PlotRange\[Rule]All]


\
\>", "Input",
